nothing about this.

00:40:36.310 --> 00:40:38.070
How would she feel?

00:40:38.070 --> 00:40:43.400 position:56%
And she went off to Ireland and sort
of got madder and madder and madder.

00:40:43.400 --> 00:40:47.070
And her father was dead but
her mother was still alive

00:40:47.070 --> 00:40:50.810
