family, the Rogers family.

00:41:02.310 --> 00:41:09.270
Her daughter, Tamara, went and
interviewed her grandmother.

00:41:09.270 --> 00:41:14.410
Her grandmother was very
uncomfortable talking about this,

00:41:14.410 --> 00:41:19.690
