crazy when it rains [laughter].

00:41:58.430 --> 00:42:02.310 position:56%
And then he came back and he said --

00:42:02.310 --> 00:42:07.290
he began telling his
friends and they all knew.

00:42:07.290 --> 00:42:10.160
Grafton had not forgotten.

00:42:10.160 --> 00:42:15.240
